 Christ shall be in it, and </div><div class="t m26c x61 h2d y18f4 ff4 fsa fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">if Christ is in us, and we in him, the praises and prayers </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
